&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://app.smore.com/n/zqt8c-bogan-weekly-news#b7suj6dsz8"&gt;View original newsletter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">b7suj6dsz8</guid><pubDate>Fri, 31 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Kiwanis Holiday Food Drive for TOPSS</title><link>https://app.smore.com/n/zqt8c-bogan-weekly-news#bjqvo7kz71</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Bogan K-Kids is collecting donations for the &lt;strong&gt;Kiwanis Holiday Food Drive&lt;/strong&gt; to benefit families served by TOPSS (Talawanda Oxford Pantry and Social Services). Donations can be brought to Bogan &lt;strong&gt;October 27th-November 7th&lt;/strong&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Requested items include:
- Canned Green Beans
- Cream of Mushroom Soup
- Cream of Chicken Soup
- Baking Mixes
- Mac &amp;amp; Cheese
- Crispy Onions
- Hygiene Products (Shampoo, Soap, Toothpaste, Deodorant, etc.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contact Ms. Currier or Mrs. Bryan with questions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Add to Calendar:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&amp;text=Kiwanis%20Holiday%20Food%20Drive%20Collection%20Period&amp;dates=20241027T000000/20241027T235900&amp;details=Bogan%20K-Kids%20is%20collecting%20donations%20for%20the%20%2A%2AKiwanis%20Holiday%20Food%20Drive%2A%2A%20to%20benefit%20families%20served%20by%20TOPSS%20%28Talawanda%20Oxford%20Pantry%20and%20Social%20Services%29.%20Donations%20can%20be%20brought%20to%20Bogan%20%2A%2AOctob&amp;location=Bogan%20Elementary%20School"&gt;Google Calendar&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href="data:text/calendar;charset=utf-8,BEGIN%3AVCALENDAR%0AVERSION%3A2.0%0ABEGIN%3AVEVENT%0ADTSTART%3A20241027T000000%0ADTEND%3A20241027T235900%0ASUMMARY%3AKiwanis%20Holiday%20Food%20Drive%20Collection%20Period%0ADESCRIPTION%3ABogan%20K-Kids%20is%20collecting%20donations%20for%20the%20%2A%2AKiwanis%20Holiday%20Food%20Drive%2A%2A%20to%20benefit%20families%20served%20by%20TOPSS%20%28Talawanda%20Oxford%20Pantry%20and%20Social%20Services%29.%20Donations%20can%20be%20brought%20to%20Bogan%20%2A%2AOctob%0ALOCATION%3ABogan%20Elementary%20School%0AEND%3AVEVENT%0AEND%3AVCALENDAR"&gt;iCal&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href="https://outlook.live.com/calendar/0/deeplink/compose?subject=Kiwanis%20Holiday%20Food%20Drive%20Collection%20Period&amp;startdt=20241027T000000&amp;enddt=20241027T235900&amp;body=Bogan%20K-Kids%20is%20collecting%20donations%20for%20the%20%2A%2AKiwanis%20Holiday%20Food%20Drive%2A%2A%20to%20benefit%20families%20served%20by%20TOPSS%20%28Talawanda%20Oxford%20Pantry%20and%20Social%20Services%29.%20Donations%20can%20be%20brought%20to%20Bogan%20%2A%2AOctob&amp;location=Bogan%20Elementary%20School"&gt;Outlook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
